        <item>
            <title>Microsoft 积极开发 Vision Pro 软件   VR/AR 实境用 Copilot、Teams、Word、Excel</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/03/microsoft-vision-pro-office/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-vision-pro-office</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/03/microsoft-vision-pro-office/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2024 06:10:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple VisionPro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AR/VR]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VisionOS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1218200</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前 Apple Vision Pro 正式在美国正式开放预购，半小时内已宣告售罄（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/22/apple-vision-pro-preorder/vr-mr-ar/">相关报道</a>）。在 Apple Vision Pro 正式出货之前，Microsoft 已发表公告，表示将会于 VisionOS App Store 推出 Microsoft Teams、Microsoft Office 系列、Outlook、OneNote 等应用程式。</p><p>据中国媒体报道，用户一收到 Vision Pro 就能够立即于 App Store 下载 Microsoft 的应用程式；与 Micrsoft 相比，Apple 自己的 iWork 办公软件初期仅有 Keynote 一款支援 Vision Pro。除此之外，Microsoft 更在 Vision Pro 推出旗下 AI「Copilot」。</p><p>Apple Vision Pro 用家可以在 Vision Pro 上沉浸式使用 PowerPoint 制作幻灯片和简报。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_01706663024630-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_01706663024630-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_01706663024630.png 975w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>透过 Apple Vision Pro 上的 Word，用家可以不受外界干扰，专心处理眼前的文件。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_21706663103334-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_21706663103334-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_21706663103334.png 975w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Microsoft 亦在 Vision Pro 上提供 Teams 应用程式，协助用家与工作伙伴使用视像对话。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_31706663151700-694x391.png" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_31706663151700-694x391.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gabo_31706663151700.png 975w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/microsoft-365-blog/announcing-microsoft-365-apps-available-on-apple-vision-pro/ba-p/4042505">Microsoft</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/02/apple-vision-pro-over-600-native-apps/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Vision Pro 今日美国上市，官方公布专属程式已超过 600 款</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/02/apple-vision-pros-gesture-controls-can-easily-be-interrupted-by-people-around-you/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Vision Pro 海外测试，手势操作会被他人轻易干扰</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/01/lightning/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Lightning 未死   Vision Pro 发现「肥版 Lightning」接头</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/03/microsoft-vision-pro-office/vr-mr-ar/">Microsoft 积极开发 Vision Pro 软件   VR/AR 实境用 Copilot、Teams、Word、Excel</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
