        <item>
            <title>全新电动 MINI Cooper 抵港   HEY MINI 语音互动车箱体验</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/02/mini-cooper-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mini-cooper-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/02/mini-cooper-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 12:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mini cooper]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1218473</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>全新电动 MINI Cooper 推出了一款设计更为简约且现代化的车型，同时保留了 MINI 经典外观。该车型注重于简洁设计美学，并以「至简 · 致形」为设计理念，旨在提供一种回归本质的驾驶体验。车内一大亮点是其首创的 240 毫米特大圆形 OLED 中控屏，提供了一种与众不同的互动式触控体验。车内空间设计保持了充足的留白，强调简约主义。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218478" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0013-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0013-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0013-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0018-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0018-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0018-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218481" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0026-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0026-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0026-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新电动 MINI Cooper 具有 JCW（John Cooper Works）风格的设计元素，包括专属的赛车条纹、鬼面罩、尾翼和门边脚踏饰条，这些都强调了其运动化特征。此外，车型还配备了 18 吋的高效能轻量再生铝轮圈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218490" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0014-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0014-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 MINI Cooper 亦注重数码化体验，搭载了全新的 MINI Operating System 9 配以<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>240mm 特大圆形 OLED 互动式触控萤幕，提供多种体验模式，使驾驶者可以根据心情和需求选择不同的驾驶模式。上半部显示车辆资讯，如行车速度或油量 /电量，而导航、多媒体、电话功能等项目选单则配置在 OLED 萤幕的下半部分，整体介面操作就像智慧手机清晰、直觉。 车内更有语音助理功能，说出「HEY MINI!」或按压方向盘上的语音按钮，语音助理随即现身服务。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218475" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0011-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0011-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0011-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218474" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0009-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0009-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0009-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218476" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0001-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0001-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车辆的安全配置也得到了全面升级，包括多种驾驶辅助和停车辅助科技，以保障行车安全。智慧驾驶辅助系统设主动车道维持辅助、盲点侦测警示、车道偏离警示、车侧防撞辅助等多种功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218484" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0006-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0006-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0006-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0003-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0003-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新电动 MINI Cooper 将采用 MINI Digital Key Plus 数码钥匙，透过 MINI App，相容智能手机/ 手表可变身成为车匙。当有关装置靠近 MINI，头尾欢迎灯将会亮起并自动解锁车辆，当驾驳者离开 MINI 时，车辆将自动上锁。透过超宽频技术 (ultra-widebanc)，即使手机在背囊或口袋中，仍可使用数码钥匙功能。<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218479" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0012-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0012-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0012-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车辆的内饰选材考虑到动物友善，座椅表面采用 100% 再生针织面料，旨在提供奢华而舒适的触感。空间配置方面，车辆后座可根据需要进行灵活配置，容积更可扩展至最高 800 公升，满足不同的储物需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218483" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0022-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0022-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218486" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0030-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0030-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0030.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218487" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0034-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0034-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0034.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MINI 还为车主提供了智慧个人语音助理，通过简单的语音指令即可控制车内多项功能，提升了驾驶的便利性和乐趣。总体而言，全新电动 MINI Cooper 以其简约设计、先进技术和对可持续性的承诺，开启了 MINI 品牌的新篇章。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0004-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0004-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0004.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218489" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0005-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0005-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218482" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0031-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0031-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire0031-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车价：HK$279,800（一换一价格）</p><p>价格适用期限：2024 年 3 月，至 5 月</p><div class="page" title="Page 1"><div class="section"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p>长度/宽度/高度：3,858/1,756/1,460 毫米</p><p>轴距：2,526 毫米</p><p>输出功率：218 马力</p><p>扭矩：330 牛顿米</p><p>0 – 100 公里/小时加速时间：6.7 秒</p><p>驱动系统：前轮驱动</p><p>电池容量：54.2 千瓦时</p><p>续航里程：402 公里（WLTP 测试标准）</p></div></div></div></div><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/26/xiaomi-su7-ev-28-dec-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">官方微博开启车章曝光，小米 SU7 电动车 28/12 发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/toyota-recalled-bz3-ev-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">剩余电量显示比实际高，一汽丰田召回 2.5 万部安全隐患 bZ3 电动车</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/02/mini-cooper-2/life-tech/auto/">全新电动 MINI Cooper 抵港   HEY MINI 语音互动车箱体验</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
